# At the time reached within a narration.
#: {{usex|lang=en|'''Now''', he remembered why he had come.&nbsp;&nbsp; He '''now''' asked her whether she had made pudding.&nbsp;&nbsp; The pudding was '''now''' ready to be served.}}
# {{non-gloss definition|In the context of urgency.}}
#: {{usex|lang=en|'''Now''' listen, we must do something about this.}}
